               <ce:section-title id="st145">Acknowledgements</ce:section-title>
               <ce:para id="p0185" view="all">We express our gratitude to all the teachers and classmates of Karst Ecological Restoration Research Group involved in the fieldwork and laboratory procedures. We also extend our thanks to Mo Jiawei and Qin Huiyuan from the Maolan National Nature Reserve for their assistance during fieldwork. Finally, we are grateful to the reviewer for their valuable feedback.</ce:para>
            </ce:acknowledgment>
